Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.71,1:31:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm noticing things that I've denied\Nbefore, but it seems like such a
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.32,1:32:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,narciss. always about me and I'm\Nanalyzing everything about myself all
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.00,1:32:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the time.\N>> Well, that's a phase and then you try
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.28,1:32:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,first you understand the ego, you\Nunravel it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.92,1:32:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah.\N>> Then you take it apart. Once it's been
