Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.84,1:32:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's important period of\Ninvestigation to know understand of
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.48,1:32:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,course what you're investigating\Nprimarily is the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.76,1:32:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> uh but uh to disassemble it uh is first\Nto become familiar with it. So I think
