Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.40,1:33:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of one's own ego and how it\Ngot to be that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.84,1:33:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the contributions of the various people\Nand the various cultures and
