Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.88,1:37:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So that\NOh god.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.15,1:37:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again for the tremendous gift\Nof being with you this entire day. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.48,1:37:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful gift\Nto be with all such wonderful people for
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.23,1:37:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole day. We share our our experience\Nof each other. Each one of us is seen
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.36,1:38:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,back and forth in the other one's eyes\Nand reflected back and forth. So as his
