Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.00,1:38:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,forth until we all become sort of enshed\Nin one unity.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.08,1:38:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless us everyone. We give thanks to\Nthee oh Lord for thy presence.
